title: 11: I've been traveling the country ALONE ...
description: What's Up F*ckers!!! It's been a whole month since Sadie has hopped on the pod. Although this isn't for no reason ... in this episode Sadie explains WTF she's been up to and the big turn her life has taken. From crashing her new car Tom the Toyota, getting lost with crackheads, and almost getting kidnapped. Sadie is sharing all the stories from these trips she's been taking all Febuary. Grab some snacks and listen tf up because was that TMI is back!!!
